Suspected All Progressives Congress, APC, leaders in Esan West Local Government Area, LGA, were on Saturday caught throwing money at some group of voters, mostly women. Voters at polling units 9, 10, 11, in Ward 4, Esan West electorate were seen fighting over the cash. DAILY POST understands that the money was brought in by party leaders as a way of swaying the voters to vote for the party. However, their aim of buying votes at the units was unsuccessful. Watch videoâ€¦
